Pembrolizumab versus chemotherapy for patients with esophageal squamous cell 
carcinoma enrolled in the randomized KEYNOTE-181 trial in Asia.

Cao Y(1), Qin S(2), Luo S(3), Li Z(4), Cheng Y(5), Fan Y(6), Sun Y(7), Yin X(8), 
Yuan X(9), Li W(10), Liu T(11), Hsu CH(12), Lin X(13), Kim SB(14), Kojima T(15), 
