Tobacco Use and Treatment of Tobacco Dependence Among People With Human 
Immunodeficiency Virus: A Practical Guide for Clinicians.

Reddy KP(1)(2)(3)(4), Kruse GR(1)(4)(5), Lee S(2), Shuter J(6), Rigotti 
NA(1)(4)(5)(7).

